<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>MediaLab Studio Template</title>
  </head>
  <body style="margin: 0; min-height: 100vh; background: radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(251,146,60,0.18), transparent 24%), linear-gradient(150deg, #fff7ed 0%, #fff1f2 46%, #f8fafc 100%); font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;">
    <div id="studio-hero" class="ml-container" style="position: absolute; left: 58px; top: 44px; width: min(1090px, calc(100vw - 116px)); height: 350px; border-radius: 40px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 38px 120px rgba(120, 53, 15, 0.15);">
      <section class="ml-content" data-import-type="div" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; padding: 42px; box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 26px; background: linear-gradient(145deg, #fffaf5 0%, #fed7aa 100%); color: #431407;">
        <div style="max-width: 60%;">
          <div style="display: inline-flex; padding: 10px 16px; border-radius: 999px; background: rgba(194,65,12,0.08); color: #9a3412; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase;">Creative Agency</div>
          <h1 style="margin: 20px 0 12px; font-size: 58px; line-height: 0.94; letter-spacing: -0.05em;">A warm, editorial front page for a modern studio.</h1>
          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.72; color: rgba(67,20,7,0.78);">This one is built for agencies, production houses, or boutique brands that want a high-trust site with softer luxury energy and strong structure.</p>
          <div style="margin-top: 26px; display: flex; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
            <a href="#" style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 14px 22px; border-radius: 18px; background: #431407; color: #fff7ed; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 800;">See Services</a>
            <a href="#" style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 14px 22px; border-radius: 18px; border: 1px solid rgba(67,20,7,0.18); color: #7c2d12; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 800;">Start a Project</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="width: 280px; border-radius: 30px; padding: 22px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.72); display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between;">
          <div style="font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #b45309;">Studio Snapshot</div>
          <div>
            <div style="font-size: 34px; font-weight: 800; color: #431407;">18 partners</div>
            <div style="margin-top: 10px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.65; color: #7c2d12;">A polished front-end starter with elegant cards, service blocks, and premium call-to-action rhythm.</div>
          </div>
          <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
            <span style="padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: 999px; background: #fff7ed; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700;">Brand</span>
            <span style="padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: 999px; background: #fff7ed; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700;">Web</span>
            <span style="padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: 999px; background: #fff7ed; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700;">Launch</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div id="studio-services" class="ml-container" style="position: absolute; left: 58px; top: 428px; width: min(1090px, calc(100vw - 116px)); height: 292px; border-radius: 34px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 28px 90px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.09);">
      <section class="ml-content" data-import-type="div" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; padding: 26px; box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; gap: 16px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);">
        <div style="flex: 1; border-radius: 28px; padding: 24px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #fff7ed 100%);">
          <div style="font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #c2410c;">Identity</div>
          <h2 style="margin: 16px 0 10px; font-size: 30px; line-height: 1.04; color: #431407;">Brand systems that feel intentional.</h2>
          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; color: #7c2d12;">A full service block for visual direction, tone, and positioning with enough polish to feel client-ready.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="flex: 1; border-radius: 28px; padding: 24px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff7ed 0%, #ffedd5 100%);">
          <div style="font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #b45309;">Web Design</div>
          <h2 style="margin: 16px 0 10px; font-size: 30px; line-height: 1.04; color: #431407;">Sites with editorial layout and modern flow.</h2>
          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; color: #7c2d12;">Use this section to frame your process, outcomes, and why your studio approach stands apart.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="flex: 1; border-radius: 28px; padding: 24px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff7ed 0%, #fde68a 100%);">
          <div style="font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #a16207;">Launch Support</div>
          <h2 style="margin: 16px 0 10px; font-size: 30px; line-height: 1.04; color: #431407;">Sharper handoff, launch, and growth touchpoints.</h2>
          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; color: #7c2d12;">A strong middle section for retaining the premium tone while still feeling welcoming and easy to customize.</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div id="studio-cta" class="ml-container" style="position: absolute; left: 58px; top: 752px; width: min(1090px, calc(100vw - 116px)); height: 208px; border-radius: 32px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(180, 83, 9, 0.14);">
      <section class="ml-content" data-import-type="div" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; padding: 30px 34px; box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 22px; background: linear-gradient(145deg, #431407 0%, #7c2d12 100%); color: #fff7ed;">
        <div>
          <div style="font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(255,237,213,0.72);">Ready to adapt</div>
          <h2 style="margin: 12px 0 10px; font-size: 40px; line-height: 1.02;">Launch a refined agency site in minutes.</h2>
          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.65; color: rgba(255,237,213,0.82);">Replace the copy, swap brand colors, and publish a warm premium website that feels custom from the start.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="#" style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-width: 190px; padding: 16px 22px; border-radius: 20px; background: #fff7ed; color: #431407; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 900;">Book Discovery</a>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
